headline: ALB- A Screaming Bargain in the Lithium Space
summary: Our favorite theme heading into 2025 was “Last Shall Be First,” with healthcare and materials as our top two sectors. So, let’s talk about Albemarle Corp. (ALB), the world’s largest and lowest-cost lithium producer, says Tom Hayes, editor of HedgeFundTips.
